headline: JP Morgan starts on International Paper at ‘overweight’, calls Smurfit top pick
summary: Investing.com -- JP Morgan initiated coverage on International Paper with an Overweight rating and a $59 price target, citing the company’s new profitability strategy and the potential benefits from its acquisition of DS Smith.
